prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "Admin can add a new company",
      "evidence_quote": "Admin can ◾ Add a new company"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Admin can delete/update a company",
      "evidence_quote": "Admin can ◾ Delete/update a company"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Admin keeps track of students interested in placements",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Keeps track of students interested in placements"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Admin can add a new training for students",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Add a new training for students (which is demanded by many companies)"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Admin can update/delete a training",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Update/delete a training (which are not demanded by many companies), etc."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "User can register for a particular job",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Register for a particular job"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "User can register for a particular company",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Register for a particular company"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "User can undertake a training",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Undertake a training"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "User can submit resume",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Submit resume"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "User can update resume",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Update resume, etc."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Company can register in the placement office",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Register in the placement office"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Company can view student resume",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ View Student resume"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Company can recruit a student with good resume and skills",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Recruit a student with good resume and skills"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Company can recruit a student trained in a specific area",
      "evidence_quote": "◾ Recruit a student trained in a specific area, etc. (Figures 31.1–31.8)"
    }
  ]
}

